*
 * Gives an item to a player.
 * @example
 * let give = new Give(
 *   new Player('Mike'),
 *   new Item('apple'),
 *   64,
 *   0,
 *   {...}
 * );
 * @see http://minecraft.gamepedia.com/Commands#give
